collection.name: NFT Bored Bunny
collection.description:
Bored Bunny is a collection of 4999 unique 3D well-designed Bunnies - Sold out in 17 minutes.
Floyd Mayweather, DJ Khaled, David Dobrik, Umar Kamani, Chantel Jeffries and many more celebrities have already joined the project.

Every Bored Bunny holder will receive a Bored Bad Bunny (our next collection) for free.
